oes, radishes, fennel, lettuce and mint; \nseason with salt and pepper. Add enough of the dressing to coat the salad (you may have extra dressing); \ntoss to thoroughly combine and season with salt and pepper to taste. \nDivide the finished salad between 2 plates. \nServe with the goat cheese toast on the side. \nEnjoy!",
